RailsQuality
===========

Rails Quality is a rails plugin with a rake task that runs several code quality tools.

Current code quality tools:
Flog
Flay
Roodi

The tools have been configured with thresholds that I have tested on a couple apps that I work on.


Installation
============
script/plugin install git://github.com/nathanhumbert/rails_quality.git


Example
=======
rake quality:test


